OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening, especially in the
OL,7,Fwest, with some patchy rain in places.
OL,8,FThe rain tending to ease overnight
OL,9,Fwith some clear spells developing by
OL,10,Fdawn. A fresher night than last night,
OL,11,Fespecially in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,14,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,15,Fenough to give the odd light shower
OL,16,Ffrom time to time. Feeling a little
OL,17,Ffresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
